VOTE-BUYING has been observed at Polling Unit 001, Ward 8, Ifofin Ilesha. The polling unit is that of the Minister of Interior, Rauf Aregbesola, who is yet to show up. The vote-buying is been coordinated by a man seated on a motorcycle. Some women were seen gathered around him in a frantic effort to get their share of the money he was disbursing. The ICIRâ€™s reporter spoke to one of the beneficiaries but she refused to disclose her name. The woman confirmed she got N5,000 from agents of the All Progressives Congress (APC). As of the time of filing this report, the location where the money is being shared has changed.